## 4. External Interface Requirements

### 4.1 User Interfaces

#### 4.1.1 Main Application Window
- **Window Title**: "ðŸŽ¨ AI Resume Generator Pro"
- **Dimensions**: 950x750 pixels
- **Background**: Gradient from light pink to white
- **Font**: Segoe UI (primary), fallback to system sans-serif

#### 4.1.2 Input Section
- **Name Field**: Single-line text entry, required
- **Email Field**: Single-line text entry, optional
- **Phone Field**: Single-line text entry, optional
- **Education Field**: Multi-line scrolled text (5 lines visible)
- **Skills Field**: Multi-line scrolled text (5 lines visible)
- **Experience Field**: Multi-line scrolled text (8 lines visible)

#### 4.1.3 Output Section
- **Resume Display**: Scrolled text area (15 lines visible)
- **Read-only**: Users cannot directly edit output
- **Font**: Monospace for consistent formatting

#### 4.1.4 Buttons
- **Generate Resume**: Large prominent button (220x50 pixels)
- **Save Input Data**: Secondary action button
- **Load Input Data**: Secondary action button
- **Save to Collection**: Secondary action button
- **Load from Collection**: Secondary action button
- **Export to PDF**: Action button
- **Hover Effect**: All buttons darken on hover

### 4.2 Hardware Interfaces
- **Display**: Standard computer monitor (minimum 950x750 resolution)
- **Input Devices**: Keyboard and mouse/trackpad
- **Storage**: Local disk drive for database and PDF files

### 4.3 Software Interfaces

#### 4.3.1 Python Runtime
- **Component**: Python Interpreter
- **Version**: 3.12 or higher
- **Purpose**: Execute application code

#### 4.3.2 Tkinter Library
- **Component**: GUI Framework
- **Purpose**: Render user interface
- **Interface**: Python API calls

#### 4.3.3 SQLite Database
- **Component**: Database Engine
- **File**: resumes.db
- **Purpose**: Store resume data locally
- **Tables**:
  - `resumes`: Input data storage
  - `generated_resumes`: Generated resume storage

#### 4.3.4 Transformers Library
- **Component**: Hugging Face Transformers
- **Model**: google/flan-t5-small
- **Purpose**: AI-powered text generation
- **Optional**: System works without this if unavailable

#### 4.3.5 ReportLab Library
- **Component**: PDF Generation Engine
- **Purpose**: Create PDF documents from resume text
- **Output**: Standard PDF files

#### 4.3.6 PyTorch
- **Component**: Machine Learning Framework
- **Version**: 2.2.0 or higher
- **Purpose**: Backend for AI model inference

### 4.4 Communications Interfaces
- **None**: Application operates entirely offline
- **No Network Required**: All processing is local

