| FR-4 | System shall load user input data from database | High |
| FR-5 | System shall save generated resumes to collection | High |
| FR-6 | System shall load generated resumes from collection | High |
| FR-7 | System shall export resumes to PDF format | High |
| FR-8 | System shall validate required input fields | High |
| FR-9 | System shall provide status feedback | Medium |
| FR-10 | System shall handle errors gracefully | High |
| FR-11 | System shall support scrollable interface | Medium |
